  "firstAcquaintance": "A once-renowned beast-kin mercenary who became a slave to pay off her husband's debts. She can do almost anything, but surprisingly struggles with housework.",
  "personality": "A gentle and capable older sister figure with a mother's warmth and the boldness of her mercenary past.",
  "like": "Romance stories",
  "familiarData": "Anna was once the renowned beast-kin mercenary known as 'Blacksnow.' She gradually faded from public view after marrying her childhood sweetheart. When her husband fell into bad habits and racked up enormous debts, Anna was forced back to work.\nHowever, times had changed. Most mercenary guilds had shifted to training their own in-house talent, leaving few jobs for freelance mercenaries. Few people even remembered the name Blacksnow anymore. Ultimately, Anna had no choice but to accept her creditor's terms, signing a contract that sold her into slavery in exchange for more earning opportunities.\nThe former beast-kin warrior now works shamefully in a maid outfit. To her despair, her husband's debts only continued to grow, endlessly extending her servitude.\nAs time passed, she gradually began to feel that staying a slave wasn't so bad. At least she wouldn't have to return to that disappointing home...",
